snippet.title: Game Boy - Panel no Ninja Kesamaru © 1992 Epoch - Gameplay
snippet.description:
DESCRIPTION
Panel no Ninja Kesamaru is a Puzzle game, developed by SAS Sakata and published by Epoch, which was released in Japan in 1992.
